        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>political ideologies and attitudes [300055513], political concepts [300055490], social science concepts [300239103], Associated Concepts (hierarchy name) [300055126], Associated Concepts Facet [300264086]</Parent_String>
